I just noticed an error in one of my PR, it needs to be
if (inexactSeek && selectedDuration / (int) DateUtils.SECOND_IN_MILLIS % 10 == 5) {
Otherwise the seek durations get rounded up when opening the settings, even if inexact seek is disabled

